'''Target of an Assassi'''n ni film yo mu 1977 iyobowe na Peter Collinson ikinwamo na Anthony Quinn na John Phillip Law<ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/us/film671740.html</ref> . yafatiwe amashusho muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]] mu 1976 ikitwa '''''Tigers Don't Cry''''' ariko ntabwo yashyizwe ahagaragara muri [[Amerika]] imyaka hafi icyenda. andi mazina  arimo ''African Rage''<ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/271847-target-of-an-assassin</ref>, ''The Long Shot'', and ''Fatal Assassin''..  Ukurikije igitabo cya  Jon Burmeister cyitwa ''Running Scared''<ref>https://trakt.tv/movies/target-of-an-assassin-1977</ref>. 

