== Umugambi ==
Filime yakiniwe mubitaro byo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo. Anthony Quinn wamenyekanye cyane akina nk'umuforomo w'umugabo<ref>https://www.cinemaclock.com/movies/target-of-an-assassin-1977</ref>, Hobday, washinzwe kwita kuri perezida w’amahanga (Simon Sabela). Hamwe n’iterabwoba ryinshi ryangiza ubuzima bwe, umuyobozi arinzwe cyane kumasaha. Hobday abasha gushimuta umurwayi we ku nyungu z'umuntu ku giti cye<ref>https://prapullapolymers.com/c7rc7b/rvssyi8.php?id=target-of-an-assassin</ref>, atazi ko sniper yahawe akazi agerageza guhitana ubuzima bw'umuyobozi w’amahanga igihe yari afunzwe na Hobday<ref>https://www.cinematerial.com/movies/target-of-an-assassin-i75307/p/milotitd</ref>. Ibi biganisha kumurongo wamatsiko y'imigambi iganisha kumiterere yikirere hamwe n'imodoka ya kabili kumusozi muremure<ref>https://www.mymovierack.com/show/target-of-an-assassin</ref>.

